headline: CoStar Group to Host Investor Day on Thursday, December 5, 2024
summary: WASHINGTON, November 19, 2024--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, and analytics in the property markets, will host an Investor Day on Thursday, December 5, 2024, from 9:00 a.m. to 2:30 p.m. ET in-person in Richmond, Virginia, and online via webcast. The event will feature presentations, engagement opportunities with CoStar Group’s leadership team and a tour of the Company’s global campus.
